Evil_Superman wrote:maybe I missed it but what app did you use?I used Plan B for Android, installed to the phone after it went missing.I pinged the phone again and its location was centered on Terminal 1, but only accurate to 1600m so I assumed it was inside the terminal, hopefully inside the lost and found office, perhaps in a box with other lost phones. I called down there and sure enough, they had it. They requested I call it from another line to confirm ownership and what a sweet sound it was to hear that ringer going off in the background. Just need to create a FedEx account and they'll ship it up.And I'll definitely take a stab at a writeup with pictures.
